<noinclude>
== Module Template ==

This template renders an infobox for module pages. It automatically loads data from [[Module:Modules_data]] based on the page name.

=== Automatic Data Loading ===

When used as <code><nowiki>{{Module}}</nowiki></code>, the template automatically queries [[Module:Modules_data]] using <code><nowiki>{{PAGENAME}}</nowiki></code> as the lookup key. No parameters are required on module pages that exist in the data module.

=== Manual Override (Backward Compatible) ===

All parameters can be manually specified to override the automatic data:

<pre>
{{Module
  | title1 = Example
  | image1 = Example.jpg
  | caption-image1 = Example
  | cost = Example
  | weight = Example
  | required_tech_level = Example
  | utility_module = Example
  | requirement = Example
  | energy_use = Example
  | speed = Example
  | critical_hit_chance = Example
  | accuracy = Example
  | firing_rate = Example
  | shield_deflection = Example
  | armor_deflection = Example
  | energy_efficiency = Example
  | energy_drain_deflection = Example
  | bounty_enhanced = Example
  | experience_enhanced = Example
  | defensive_merit = Example
}}
</pre>

